74
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:32,600
Then I'd better teach you properly tonight.

75
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,279
You...

76
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,519
Come here.

77
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,679
What kind of drink would
you like to have, sir?

78
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:49,799
I'll help you choose.

79
00:04:50,119 --> 00:04:51,200
Pick what you like.

80
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,279
Here.

81
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,480
Let me give you a sip.

82
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,480
Professor You...

83
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,040
That's it?

84
00:05:14,679 --> 00:05:16,600
No secret techniques from the vault?

85
00:05:21,559 --> 00:05:22,559
Handsome...

86
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:24,839
you're up.

87
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:29,160
Then I'm adding ice, okay?

88
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:32,119
Might feel a little cold.

89
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,280
Since Teacher You is willing to teach,

90
00:05:57,239 --> 00:05:59,239
let's switch to a better classroom.

91
00:06:02,239 --> 00:06:03,239
Sure.

92
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:12,040
If you want to learn,

93
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:15,000
be good.

94
00:06:21,239 --> 00:06:22,880
How is Teacher You going to teach me?

95
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,640
Hm.

96
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,000
What...

97
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:29,040
Is President Fan jealous?

98
00:06:30,119 --> 00:06:31,320
I'm willing to do anything,

99
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,279
but I don't do jealousy.

100
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,399
Right.

101
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:39,480
Our President Fan never gets jealous.

102
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:44,600
Happy birthday, babe.

103
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:49,760
Then teach me how to be happy.

104
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:56,920
All that stuff I just showed
you, did you catch any of it?

105
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:00,519
Come here.

106
00:07:13,679 --> 00:07:15,519
What would you like to drink, sir?

107
00:07:16,559 --> 00:07:17,559
Shulang.

108
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,000
Mm?

109
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:21,640
Any requests, sir?

110
00:07:25,119 --> 00:07:26,519
Whatever you like.

111
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:56,279
Teacher You's mixing is a little off.

112
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,040
It's too bland.

113
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,679
Someone needs to be punished.

114
00:08:13,119 --> 00:08:14,480
How do you want to punish me?

115
00:08:25,799 --> 00:08:26,799
Fan Xiao...

116
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,480
Your fiancée is here.

117
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,200
Don't stop, Teacher You.

118
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,479
Your fiancée's here!

119
00:08:37,719 --> 00:08:38,520
Fan Xiao...

120
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:39,880
I don't have a fiancée.

121
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:45,159
Do you want me to keep away from her?

122
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:47,640
No.
Let's go.

123
00:08:48,401 --> 00:08:49,601
We'll go take a look together.

124
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:52,919
Wait.

125
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,798
This is the birthday gift
I've prepared for you.

126
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:06,799
It's not expensive.

127
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,080
Don't think too much of it.

128
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:23,559
