129
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,400
With you around,

130
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,080
Every moment is happy.

131
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,359
I love it.

132
00:09:31,479 --> 00:09:32,559
I'll wear it all the time.

133
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,200
