135
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,159
Let's go.

136
00:09:38,599 --> 00:09:39,760
Go meet your “fiancée.”

137
00:09:44,559 --> 00:09:45,919
I don't have a fiancée.

138
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,880
Whatever they say, don't believe it.

139
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,400
Okay.

140
00:09:57,500 --> 00:10:01,000
(Episode 7)

141
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:03,479
Big brother, second brother...
Xiao's here.

142
00:10:04,479 --> 00:10:05,159
See?

143
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:07,000
Bathroom breaks aren't that long.

144
00:10:14,239 --> 00:10:15,239
Little third,

145
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,238
you've been gone seven or eight months,

146
00:10:17,239 --> 00:10:18,479
and never came to see us.

147
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:20,479
Since you wouldn't come back,

148
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,158
we bought tickets and flew over

149
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:23,559
to celebrate your birthday.

150
00:10:24,479 --> 00:10:26,239
Big bro, second bro...

151
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,640
why didn't you tell me you were coming?

152
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,376
I would've picked you up at the airport.

153
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,199
We wanted to surprise you,

154
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:33,679
So,

155
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,678
we had Uncle Xu pick us up.

156
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:36,999
You boys are grown men,

157
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,479
and still you play these games.

158
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:41,279
But seeing you close and affectionate,

159
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:43,400
I'll speak for the chairman
and say it makes me happy.

160
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,799
Xiao Xiao,

161
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,039
it's your birthday today.

162
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:49,919
Tingting insisted on coming to celebrate
as soon as she was discharged.

163
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:52,719
She took ages choosing your gift.

164
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,679
Xiao Xiao,

165
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:04,038
thank you for taking me to
Bangkok for medical treatment.

166
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:05,880
This is the present I chose for you.

167
00:11:08,359 --> 00:11:09,359
You're too kind.

168
00:11:11,239 --> 00:11:12,239
A Huo.

169
00:11:12,479 --> 00:11:13,479
Here.

170
00:11:22,719 --> 00:11:24,359
Xiao Xiao,

171
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:28,200
aren't you going to open Tingting's gift?

172
00:11:28,679 --> 00:11:31,478
She said you often
visited her in the hospital...

173
00:11:31,479 --> 00:11:32,559
you're so thoughtful.

174
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:36,559
She put a lot of heart
into choosing that gift.

175
00:11:39,559 --> 00:11:40,559
Shulang...

176
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:41,960
Sit here.

177
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,200
Uncle Xu,

178
00:11:53,559 --> 00:11:55,359
Tingting is like my own little sister.

179
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:57,280
Taking care of her is my duty.

180
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:58,719
As for the gifts...

181
00:11:59,039 --> 00:12:00,239
There's too many.

182
00:12:00,599 --> 00:12:02,479
Let me take my time and
go through them at home.

183
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,280
Look at thi...

184
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,840
Father sent us

185
00:12:12,359 --> 00:12:14,479
to check on your investments.

186
00:12:15,119 --> 00:12:17,039
