Singapore for so long...

187
00:12:17,359 --> 00:12:18,400
Is it that…

188
00:12:18,679 --> 00:12:21,000
you've lost so much
you can't afford airfare?

189
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:23,238
Big bro's just scaring you.

190
00:12:23,239 --> 00:12:24,039
Father

191
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:25,358
only asked us to check in on you...

192
00:12:25,359 --> 00:12:26,798
if there's business trouble,

193
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,799
let us help.

194
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:30,080
You know I'm useless at work,

195
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,280
but I can help you chase girls!

196
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:39,000
This should be to your taste, Shulang.

197
00:12:41,119 --> 00:12:42,280
And this is...

198
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:45,079
Second bro, this is my...

199
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,280
Director You.

200
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:47,840
Right, right.

201
00:12:47,841 --> 00:12:49,159
I haven't introduced you...

202
00:12:49,479 --> 00:12:50,839
This is my eldest brother, Fan Bo;

203
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,200
this is my second brother, Fan Yu.

204
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:54,640
You know Vice President Xu,

205
00:12:55,479 --> 00:12:57,760
and by his side, his daughter Xu Ting.

206
00:12:58,799 --> 00:13:00,080
Big bro, second bro...

207
00:13:01,119 --> 00:13:01,799
this is

208
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:03,919
You Shulang, Office
Director of Bohai Pharma.

209
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:06,158
The drug we developed with Bohai

210
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:07,239
