211
00:13:07,799 --> 00:13:08,280
Pleasure.

212
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,599
Pleasure, pleasure.

213
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:11,319
Since he's little third's friend,

214
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,200
we'll...
Fan Xiao...

215
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:16,159
