217
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:21,039
where does that put
Father's years of friendship

218
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,080
with Uncle Xu?

219
00:13:22,239 --> 00:13:24,936
Big bro, it seems like I'm not quite
understanding what you're saying.

220
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:27,000
Since when did Tingting become my fiancée?

221
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:30,080
She's a proper young lady...

222
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:31,799
If you say that,

223
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:33,719
you'll make her cry.

224
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:35,919
Little third...

225
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,679
you forgot?

226
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:37,840
Before you left home,

227
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,839
Father said if Tingting recovered,

228
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,960
