231
00:13:46,719 --> 00:13:47,719
Director You...

232
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,400
how about we go play cards?

233
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:50,559
Let's go.
Don't go.

234
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:55,280
I only remember Father saying

235
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,798
if Miss Xu and I got along,

236
00:13:57,799 --> 00:13:59,080
we could consider an engagement.

237
00:13:59,119 --> 00:14:00,280
Tingting is excellent;

238
00:14:00,679 --> 00:14:02,679
