255
00:14:37,559 --> 00:14:38,239
It's best if you don't...
Fan Xiao...

256
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:41,119
You're going too far.

257
00:14:41,239 --> 00:14:42,239
Big bro, big bro...

258
00:14:42,479 --> 00:14:43,200
Fan Xiao...

259
00:14:43,201 --> 00:14:44,280
Watch your mouth.

260
00:14:44,520 --> 00:14:46,718
You know sister-in-law
is big bro's sore spot.

261
00:14:46,719 --> 00:14:46,960
You...

262
00:14:46,961 --> 00:14:49,280
why bring up what hurts?

263
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,000
You...

264
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:54,479
Tingting...
He— they...

265
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,679
