266
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:57,880
Tingting...

267
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:58,799
Tingting!

268
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,038
My daughter...

269
00:15:00,039 --> 00:15:02,039
is not a toy for your Fan family to bully.

270
00:15:02,239 --> 00:15:03,239
Uncle Xu...

271
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:03,840
Uncle Xu...
Don't go!

272
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:05,200
Uncle Xu...

273
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:06,320
This...

274
00:15:12,719 --> 00:15:13,719
Little third...

275
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:16,999
Xu Zhong loves stirring
the pot in front of Father.

276
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,200
Who knows what charge he'll pin on you.

277
00:15:20,119 --> 00:15:21,039
You might as well

278
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:22,759
