to my place tonight...

402
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:50,560
No.

403
00:20:50,561 --> 00:20:51,599
Don't say it.

404
00:20:51,719 --> 00:20:52,719
I won't agree.

405
00:20:53,479 --> 00:20:55,599
These days, only when I see you

406
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:56,920
when I'm holding you

407
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,640
do I feel alive.

408
00:20:59,479 --> 00:21:00,679
I mean...

409
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:02,599
I'm at your place now.

410
00:21:03,319 --> 00:21:04,319
What?

411
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:05,680
You're at my place?

412
00:21:05,681 --> 00:21:07,039
You work late every day

413
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:08,718
