421
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:21,880
Okay.

422
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,000
See you soon.

423
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,598
I need to handle Xue Baotian

424
00:21:48,599 --> 00:21:50,319
before Fan Xiao gets back,

425
00:21:51,079 --> 00:21:53,719
