429
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:13,800
I'll leave a message.

430
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:28,040
So many missed calls and
messages from Shulang.

431
00:22:40,599 --> 00:22:42,478
Fan Xiao, I'm just calling you

432
00:22:42,479 --> 00:22:43,640
to say

433
00:22:43,719 --> 00:22:46,680
I checking my email
on your computer for a moment.

434
00:22:47,119 --> 00:22:48,119
The computer?!

435
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:50,120
You didn't even set a password.

436
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:24,880
Shulang...

437
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,280
It's so dark in here.

438
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:29,199
Why not open the curtains?

439
00:23:35,520 --> 00:23:36,680
You'd better not touch me.

440
00:23:39,280 --> 00:23:41,239
What's wrong—why so mad?

441
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:44,319
Did I mess up?

442
00:23:44,359 --> 00:23:45,359
Fan Xiao...

443
00:23:46,040 --> 00:23:47,239
Don't play dumb.

444
00:23:48,239 --> 00:23:49,839
I'm only giving you one chance.

445
00:23:50,239 --> 00:23:51,880
He must've found out.

446
00:23:52,319 --> 00:23:53,719
He always means what he says.

447
00:23:54,359 --> 00:23:56,800
You know I always mean what I say.

448
00:23:57,400 --> 00:24:00,239
Lying now will only make it worse.

449
00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:02,400
You know the cost of lying.

450
00:24:03,319 --> 00:24:04,920
Better to tell the truth.

451
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:08,920
It shouldn't be that serious.

452
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:14,359
You saw that dash-cam clip?

453
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:19,000
I found it while sorting files.

454
00:24:19,760 --> 00:24:20,815
I didn't have the heart to delete it.

455
00:24:20,839 --> 00:24:21,640
When I miss you

456
00:24:21,641 --> 00:24:22,680
and you're not around,

457
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:24,560
I take a look.

458
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,358
If you don't like it,

459
00:24:27,359 --> 00:24:28,760
I'll delete it.

460
00:24:29,560 --> 00:24:30,560
Forgive me.

461
00:24:31,119 --> 00:24:32,119
Director You...

462
00:24:33,719 --> 00:24:34,719
Fan Xiao...

463
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:35,920
Then tell me:

464
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:38,719
When did you “find” that video?

465
00:24:39,479 --> 00:24:40,479
Recently.

466
00:24:40,760 --> 00:24:41,760
Yeah, recently.

467
00:24:43,199 --> 00:24:44,479
After we got together?

468
00:24:45,239 --> 00:24:46,239
Probably.

469
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:50,520
Fan Xiao...

470
00:24:50,521 --> 00:24:52,119
I checked the playback log.

471
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:54,958
After it was uploaded to your terminal,

472
00:24:54,959 --> 00:24:56,479
it was often played.

473
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:57,999
The earliest replay

474
00:24:58,000 --> 00:25:00,199
was two hours after it was recorded.

475
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:08,000
Explain to my why you open
it every night from that day on?

476
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:10,600
Don't you dare say you
already liked me then.

477
00:25:11,479 --> 00:25:13,520
Save that crap.

478
00:25:14,719 --> 00:25:16,359
Even if you don't let
me speak, I have to.

479
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:20,719
I stumbled on that clip by accident.

480
00:25:21,239 --> 00:25:22,719
At first I just glanced,

481
00:25:23,479 --> 00:25:24,800
but I couldn't stop.

482
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:27,119
It was like a magnet,

483
00:25:27,560 --> 00:25:29,479
pulling me in every minute of the day.

484
00:25:32,119 --> 00:25:34,239
Each time it sparked endless desire.

485
00:25:34,479 --> 00:25:36,520
I despised myself for it.

486
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:39,000
You were my best friend.

487
00:25:39,319 --> 00:25:40,040
How could I secretly

488
00:25:40,041 --> 00:25:41,800
lust after my friend constantly?

489
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:44,800
For a while,

490
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,280
I didn't dare see you.

491
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:50,199
When I did, I couldn't meet your gaze...

492
00:25:51,119 --> 00:25:52,479
it felt like a desecration.

493
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:53,879
But every time I resolved

494
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:55,560
to delete it,

495
00:25:56,520 --> 00:25:57,719
I hesitated so much.

496
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:01,839
I even recovered it from the
deleted files so many times.

497
00:26:04,119 --> 00:26:05,040
I can't explain

498
00:26:05,041 --> 00:26:06,599
why I did that...

499
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:10,159
why only watching that video of you

500
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:11,560
