504
00:26:19,199 --> 00:26:21,119
We'd known each other one month.

505
00:26:21,479 --> 00:26:23,136
Where would that feeling of love come from?

506
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,160
And besides...

507
00:26:24,479 --> 00:26:26,199
Weren't you straight then?

508
00:26:26,479 --> 00:26:28,759
No way one video made you switch teams.

509
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:30,400
Who wrote the rules?

510
00:26:31,280 --> 00:26:32,559
Who says within a month

511
00:26:32,560 --> 00:26:33,680
you can't fall for someone?

512
00:26:34,040 --> 00:26:35,760
