517
00:26:49,719 --> 00:26:50,719
Nonsense.

518
00:26:51,959 --> 00:26:52,959
Fan Xiao...

519
00:26:53,119 --> 00:26:55,719
I never saw you dodge my gaze,

520
00:26:56,119 --> 00:26:58,359
or feel your helplessness or guilt.

521
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:01,479
