541
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,479
The video was exciting, right?

542
00:27:58,599 --> 00:27:59,880
Then record one for me too.

543
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:14,160
Start.

544
00:28:14,839 --> 00:28:15,839
Everything off?

545
00:28:16,719 --> 00:28:17,880
All of it.

546
00:28:18,560 --> 00:28:20,400
