to offer my apology.

565
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:40,280
Hey...

566
00:29:40,560 --> 00:29:41,560
Don't.

567
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:42,760
I can't afford that.

568
00:29:46,079 --> 00:29:47,119
Say, Mr. You...

569
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:50,359
You moved mountains to
rescue a hostess, and yet...

570
00:29:50,599 --> 00:29:53,479
when it's me, you close your eyes
and let me die? Don't I deserve saving?

571
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:56,040
Isn't my fortune worth it?

572
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:58,880
A hostess?

573
00:29:59,479 --> 00:30:00,479
What hostess?

574
00:30:07,479 --> 00:30:09,160
Fan Xiao slept with you, didn't he?

575
00:30:12,479 --> 00:30:14,000
I guess I guessed right?

576
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,319
No wonder he's changed...

577
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:18,496
clinging to you like a
bodhisattva on an altar.

578
00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:20,520
Kept and worshipped.

579
00:30:22,959 --> 00:30:26,199
Someone like you can get topped?

580
00:30:28,359 --> 00:30:29,999
Guess it's not that I'm bad with women...

581
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:33,239
Since that bastard Zhang Chi

582
00:30:34,479 --> 00:30:35,400
did me,

583
00:30:35,401 --> 00:30:37,640
I can't even flirt right.

584
00:30:38,119 --> 00:30:39,119
Director You...

585
00:30:39,479 --> 00:30:41,071
do you have the same problem?

586
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:47,719
What did you need today?

587
00:30:49,199 --> 00:30:51,560
The Bohai pharma thing, right?

588
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:54,839
Yes—I wanted to ask about those returns.

589
00:30:55,040 --> 00:30:57,200
I've got some questions about how they've
been handled.

590
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,559
It's nothing...

591
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,000
just going through the motions.

592
00:31:00,359 --> 00:31:00,880
From now on,

593
00:31:01,119 --> 00:31:02,279
stock them if needed,

594
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:03,280
promote them if needed.

595
00:31:03,839 --> 00:31:05,520
If anything comes up, find me directly.

596
00:31:09,719 --> 00:31:10,520
Okay.

597
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:13,319
Thank you for cutting us some slack.

598
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:14,760
It's nothing.

599
00:31:15,199 --> 00:31:18,199
From today we're brothers in misery...

600
00:31:18,319 --> 00:31:19,239
on the same side.

601
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:20,400
And listen...

602
00:31:20,479 --> 00:31:22,160
about Fan Xiao...

603
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:24,040
let me think how to say this…

604
00:31:25,560 --> 00:31:26,759
Money, cars,

605
00:31:26,760 --> 00:31:28,760
housing—ask for what you want.

606
00:31:28,839 --> 00:31:30,640
He's loaded anyway.

607
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,000
Hello?

608
00:31:35,839 --> 00:31:36,919
Why rush me?

609
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:37,920
I just stepped out.

610
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,239
Okay, okay.
Got it, got it.

611
00:31:40,079 --> 00:31:41,079
I'm coming back now.

612
00:31:42,599 --> 00:31:43,599
Mr. Xue...

613
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:44,079
Hm?

614
00:31:44,359 --> 00:31:46,479
That hostess you mentioned...

615
00:31:46,839 --> 00:31:48,359
I rescued a hostess?

616
00:31:48,599 --> 00:31:49,599
Um…

617
00:31:50,119 --> 00:31:51,399
What hostess?

618
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,199
You misheard.

619
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,400
I'm off.

620
00:31:54,359 --> 00:31:55,719
That bastard Zhang Chi…

621
00:31:58,040 --> 00:31:58,959
Anyway...
keep your eyes open.

622
00:32:01,479 --> 00:32:02,479
I'm going.

623
00:32:03,319 --> 00:32:04,319
Bye.

624
00:32:09,560 --> 00:32:10,839
A hostess…

625
00:32:13,319 --> 00:32:14,239
Sir...

626
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:16,478
we've got all types of girls.

627
00:32:16,479 --> 00:32:18,479
What's your preference?

628
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:23,640
One moment.

629
00:32:25,079 --> 00:32:26,079
Hello?

630
00:32:26,839 --> 00:32:28,040
I have to work late today.

631
00:32:28,479 --> 00:32:30,000
I'll be back late.

632
00:32:30,040 --> 00:32:33,280
He looks upright and clean;
I thought he was decent.

633
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:34,640
Hah...

634
00:32:34,839 --> 00:32:35,839
it turns out,

635
00:32:36,079 --> 00:32:37,479
men are all the same,

636
00:32:37,560 --> 00:32:40,199
lying through their teeth to sneak around.

637
00:32:40,359 --> 00:32:42,280
Eat first—don't wait up.

638
00:32:43,079 --> 00:32:44,079
Mm.

639
00:32:46,040 --> 00:32:47,919
What type do you like?

640
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:49,479
I'll bring them in for you to choose.

641
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,839
Fresh-faced,

642
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:52,719
like recent college grads.

643
00:32:53,079 --> 00:32:54,520
Bring that type.

644
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:56,119
Sure—one moment.

645
00:32:59,959 --> 00:33:00,999
Ladies, come with me.

646
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,040
Come in.

647
00:33:11,119 --> 00:33:13,239
Greet the gentleman.

648
00:33:13,719 --> 00:33:15,880
Good evening, sir.

649
00:33:16,239 --> 00:33:17,119
Mr. You...

650
00:33:17,120 --> 00:33:19,560
Pick whoever you like.

651
00:33:20,319 --> 00:33:21,040
This one stays.
Okay.

652
00:33:21,479 --> 00:33:23,119
The rest can go.

653
00:33:23,199 --> 00:33:24,999
Enjoy your night.

654
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:26,800
Go on, go on.

655
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:34,280
Tang Xiaowan...

656
00:33:35,280 --> 00:33:37,040
That was the name you used that night,
right?

657
00:33:38,560 --> 00:33:39,560
I remember you.

658
00:33:39,719 --> 00:33:41,719
You're one of the few good people I've met.

659
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:44,400
I thought you were stupid then...

660
00:33:44,479 --> 00:33:47,040
Is it worth it for someone who you don't
know at all?

661
00:33:52,119 --> 00:33:53,119
Do what you can.

662
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,880
If I can help, I will.

663
00:33:56,560 --> 00:33:57,839
If I really can't,

664
00:33:58,760 --> 00:34:00,119
I won't force it.

665
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:06,800
You came to ask something, didn't you?

666
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,160
Yes.

667
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:12,479
Who was making a fool of me that
night?

668
00:34:13,560 --> 00:34:15,760
You only realized now were were made a
fool?

669
00:34:15,959 --> 00:34:17,360
You're such a dope.

670
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:19,080
You know

671
00:34:19,600 --> 00:34:22,080
in our line of work, we keep our mouths
shut,

672
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:24,120
or we don't eat.

673
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:25,320
I know.

674
00:34:25,959 --> 00:34:26,959
I understand.

675
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:30,080
I don't know how much

676
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:32,639
it would take for you to tell me what you
know...

677
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:35,679
You still look down on us, huh?

678
00:34:41,159 --> 00:34:43,679
Buy me a lollipop and I'll tell you.

679
00:34:45,919 --> 00:34:49,520
What made you be the only
good one I've met since I started?

680
00:35:07,719 --> 00:35:08,239
Hello?
Shulang...

681
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:11,280
why aren't you back yet?

682
00:35:11,879 --> 00:35:13,479
I kept calling but there was no answer.

683
00:35:14,080 --> 00:35:15,080
I'm fine.

684
00:35:15,479 --> 00:35:16,999
I talked to Xue Baotian today

685
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,760
about stocking items near their expiry
date.

686
00:35:19,239 --> 00:35:20,479
He let it slide.

687
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:23,159
I handled the follow-up quickly.

688
00:35:23,199 --> 00:35:25,080
Where are you? I'll pick you up.

689
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:26,600
No need.

690
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:28,320
I'm heading back.

691
00:35:30,919 --> 00:35:31,919
Fan Xiao...

692
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:34,080
Xue helped a lot this time.

693
00:35:34,239 --> 00:35:35,520
I should show some thanks.

694
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:39,520
I'm thinking of inviting him out.

695
00:35:40,719 --> 00:35:42,039
Your reputation carries weight...

696
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:44,959
call a couple of his friends
to join.

697
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:45,840
Sure.

698
00:35:45,841 --> 00:35:47,320
Whatever you say.

699
00:35:48,399 --> 00:35:49,959
I'm used to sleeping while holding you.

700
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:52,560
Without you, I can't settle.

701
00:35:53,399 --> 00:35:54,399
Okay.

702
00:36:08,040 --> 00:36:09,839
How did I lose again?

703
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:11,520
I never win with you guys.

704
00:36:11,639 --> 00:36:12,959
Then it's on me.

705
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:15,959
I brought Mr. Xue out to cheer you up.

706
00:36:16,679 --> 00:36:17,959
Happy, happy—very happy.

707
00:36:18,639 --> 00:36:20,239
Quite happy.

708
00:36:20,399 --> 00:36:22,519
As long as I'm not with that bastard Zhang
Chi,

709
00:36:22,520 --> 00:36:24,719
I'm extra happy.

710
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:27,198
Girls, booze, brothers...

711
00:36:27,199 --> 00:36:28,918
that's what life's really about.

712
00:36:28,919 --> 00:36:30,000
Mr. Xue...

713
00:36:30,879 --> 00:36:33,520
thanks for your continued
support of Bohai Pharma.

714
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:34,159
Cheers.

715
00:36:34,560 --> 00:36:35,560
You're too polite.

716
00:36:36,479 --> 00:36:38,600
President Fan, join us!

717
00:36:39,919 --> 00:36:40,159
Come on.
Sure, I'll keep you company.

718
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:42,119
Bottoms up!

719
00:36:42,120 --> 00:36:42,520
Let's drink together.
Drink up!

720
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:51,520
Let's keep going!

721
00:36:51,560 --> 00:36:53,678
I don't believe I can't win tonight.

722
00:36:53,679 --> 00:36:54,919
Keep going!

723
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:02,760
Just drinking when you lose is boring.

724
00:37:02,919 --> 00:37:06,360
How about we raise the stakes?

725
00:37:07,199 --> 00:37:08,479
Make it exciting.

726
00:37:10,520 --> 00:37:11,560
Director You...

727
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:14,320
you're growing on me.

728
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:16,359
Play— the wilder the better.

729
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:17,360
How do we play?

730
00:37:18,919 --> 00:37:19,679
President Fan...
Are you joining?

731
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:23,120
If you want, I'll join you.

732
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:24,520
Your call.

733
00:37:34,399 --> 00:37:38,080
One of these glasses has something extra.

734
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:42,479
The loser picks one at random.

735
00:37:42,719 --> 00:37:44,080
What you drink...

736
00:37:44,919 --> 00:37:46,199
is up to fate.

737
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:58,040
Xiao...

738
00:38:05,120 --> 00:38:06,360
Director You is joking.

739
00:38:07,399 --> 00:38:08,478
Don't you know him...

740
00:38:08,479 --> 00:38:09,879
he's the most law-abiding.

741
00:38:10,600 --> 00:38:11,600
After drinking,

742
00:38:11,601 --> 00:38:13,919
he won't even drive in his own courtyard.

743
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:15,840
He wouldn't play that.

744
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:17,560
He's teasing you.

745
00:38:23,639 --> 00:38:25,760
Now's not the time to take Xue down.

746
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:28,520
You think I'm taking him down?

747
00:38:29,479 --> 00:38:30,479
What else?

748
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:31,800
He's a jerk,

749
00:38:32,679 --> 00:38:34,840
but it really isn't the right time.

750
00:38:37,399 --> 00:38:39,080
Is he the only jerk?

751
00:38:40,159 --> 00:38:41,479
None of them are good people.

752
00:38:41,879 --> 00:38:43,320
They made a clown of you.

753
00:38:43,959 --> 00:38:44,959
All of them?

754
00:38:47,199 --> 00:38:49,760
I remember

755
00:38:50,159 --> 00:38:53,040
the man with the Buddha pendant.

756
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:54,919
He didn't say much,

757
00:38:55,479 --> 00:38:57,760
but I think he knew.

758
00:38:59,080 --> 00:39:00,080
You sure?

759
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:03,560
Not a hundred percent.

760
00:39:04,479 --> 00:39:07,320
But you should know, that
women's intuition is sharp.

761
00:39:07,879 --> 00:39:09,919
He didn't act on the surface,

762
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:12,679
but he's definitely no good.

763
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:21,080
Good man,

764
00:39:21,879 --> 00:39:23,080
you can't touch them.

765
00:39:23,919 --> 00:39:25,760
They're rich bastards.

766
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:27,959
Don't think about revenge.

767
00:39:28,199 --> 00:39:29,199
Stay away.

768
00:39:37,239 --> 00:39:38,239
Mr. Xue...

769
00:39:40,719 --> 00:39:43,520
That “female subordinate”
last time was fake, right?

770
00:39:44,560 --> 00:39:46,239
Hired to mess with me.

771
00:39:58,280 --> 00:40:01,840
But the spiked drink was real.

772
00:40:02,479 --> 00:40:04,800
When you watched me down that glass,

773
00:40:07,239 --> 00:40:08,958
was it fun?

774
00:40:08,959 --> 00:40:10,360
Exciting?

775
00:40:10,919 --> 00:40:12,159
หุบปากได้แล้ว. (Shut your mouths.)

776
00:40:17,879 --> 00:40:18,879
Sorry...

777
00:40:19,679 --> 00:40:21,879
I slipped into Thai in
the heat of the moment.

778
00:40:23,399 --> 00:40:24,560
Mr. Xue...

779
00:40:25,479 --> 00:40:27,479
Director You still minds what happened.

780
00:40:29,560 --> 00:40:32,199
Why don't you explain what
was going on that night...

781
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:34,280
Clear the air,

782
00:40:34,919 --> 00:40:36,256
and there'll be no misunderstanding.

783
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,280
Um… I...

784
00:40:40,239 --> 00:40:41,040
What are you sitting for?

785
00:40:41,041 --> 00:40:42,319
Grab a bottle.

786
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:43,320
Yeah.

787
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,120
Director You...

788
00:40:48,719 --> 00:40:50,159
I'm the one who messed with you.

789
00:40:51,239 --> 00:40:53,040
I don't like you.

790
00:40:53,159 --> 00:40:56,040
I think you're using Fan Xiao.

791
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:58,520
And you put on airs...

792
00:40:59,120 --> 00:41:01,479
you make him worship you.

793
00:41:06,280 --> 00:41:10,279
That night Second Young Master Xue
and I were teasing you...

794
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,280
just a joke.

795
00:41:11,479 --> 00:41:12,760
He meant no harm...

796
00:41:13,479 --> 00:41:14,520
but I did.

797
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:18,120
Even now I still can't stand you.

798
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:21,839
Do you know how much Fan
Xiao spent on your brother?

799
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:23,559
Isn't that what you're after?

800
00:41:23,560 --> 00:41:25,000
Shi Lihua, you've gone too far.

801
00:41:30,560 --> 00:41:31,560
We're leaving.

802
00:41:32,399 --> 00:41:33,840
Now's not the time to keep talking.

803
00:41:57,479 --> 00:41:58,479
Fan Xiao...

804
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:02,879
Did you take part in messing with me?

805
00:42:03,159 --> 00:42:04,479
Why would I mess with you?

806
00:42:05,560 --> 00:42:07,280
I protected you all night.

807
00:42:08,520 --> 00:42:09,520
Did you forget?

808
00:42:10,399 --> 00:42:11,800
Then why are you nervous?

809
00:42:12,679 --> 00:42:13,679
Nervous?

810
00:42:15,719 --> 00:42:17,800
I'm just worried you'll fall out with Xue

811
00:42:18,360 --> 00:42:19,719
and he'll stir up trouble.

812
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:21,840
Fan Xiao...

813
00:42:22,479 --> 00:42:23,479
Do you know...

814
00:42:25,719 --> 00:42:27,000
this spot

815
00:42:27,199 --> 00:42:28,719
behind your ear...

816
00:42:29,479 --> 00:42:31,399
when you're terrified,

817
00:42:31,959 --> 00:42:33,638
it twitches uncontrollably.

818
00:42:33,639 --> 00:42:34,959
When you hear waves,

819
00:42:35,959 --> 00:42:37,080
when you see the sea,

820
00:42:37,719 --> 00:42:38,560
in nightmares...
it does that.

821
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:42,879
It twitched three times tonight.

822
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:47,320
Don't say you're afraid
of Xue making trouble.

823
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:49,800
That level of trouble

824
00:42:50,280 --> 00:42:52,360
isn't enough to rattle you, is it?

825
00:42:52,639 --> 00:42:53,639
President Fan...

826
00:42:55,080 --> 00:42:56,879
That's how Director You deems to judge me?

827
00:43:02,479 --> 00:43:03,479
Yes.

828
00:43:04,120 --> 00:43:05,560
I don't have proof,

829
00:43:05,600 --> 00:43:07,679
but I feel awful.

830
00:43:15,600 --> 00:43:16,600
Fan Xiao...

831
00:43:18,199 --> 00:43:20,120
Let's not see each other for a while.

832
00:43:34,120 --> 00:43:35,599
In the crowd

833
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:39,159
I was spotted in an instant

834
00:43:40,280 --> 00:43:42,678
The desolation in your eyes

835
00:43:42,679 --> 00:43:45,839
Hiding the same fire inside

836
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:48,519
No need for words

837
00:43:48,520 --> 00:43:51,840
No need to ask whats right or wrong

838
00:43:52,600 --> 00:43:54,359
The moment we drew close

839
00:43:54,360 --> 00:43:57,080
The outcome was already destined

840
00:44:05,239 --> 00:44:07,760
Is the moth drawn to the light

841
00:44:08,600 --> 00:44:11,120
Or the whale sinking into the deep

842
00:44:11,719 --> 00:44:13,238
With nothing but solitary courage

843
00:44:13,239 --> 00:44:15,800
I wager it all on tomorrow

844
00:44:17,040 --> 00:44:19,799
The walls of the world

845
00:44:19,800 --> 00:44:23,080
What does it matter if I break them down

